title: Infrastructure services
category: Infrastructure & DevOps, Product & Project Management, Community & Business Development
description: We contribute to Namada in many ways, including infrastructure and marketing. Some of our services, such as RPC, REST, and API, were launched very recently, but we have been marketing Namada since 2023 or even earlier.
notes: As we mentioned, we started contributing as POSTHUMAN in the very early days of Namada and Anoma. You can find all contribution links on our GitHub, and we look forward to expanding our contributions. If you have any requests that we may fulfill, let us know!
